Adding basic finalist system.

Due to time constraints and not wanting to modify the data model, we are designating
finalists using a settings_local variable. Internal links to the finalists page will
appear when ALLOW_VOTING is disabled. settings.FINALIST_LIST is a list of game ids.

It's not pretty, but it works.
